OL,3,CBailiffs 'threatened to take disabled
OL,4,Cman's equipment'
OL,6,FAn MP has called for a crackdown on
OL,7,F"rogue bailiffs" after claims a
OL,8,Fconstituent was threatened with the
OL,9,Fremoval of disability equipment and
OL,10,Fanother left without carpets.
OL,12,FLuke Charters said firms should be put
OL,13,Fon a statutory footing to drive up
OL,14,Fstandards in the industry.
OL,16,FThe Labour MP for York Outer said
OL,17,Fvulnerable people were being made to
OL,18,Ffeel "absolutely petrified in their
OL,19,Fown homes".
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/8
