OL,3,CBailiffs 'threatened to take disabled
OL,4,Cman's equipment'
OL,6,F"Adam told me, 'it was like someone
OL,7,Fwas trying to boot down the door'. He
OL,8,Fimmediately told the bailiff that he
OL,9,Fhad a disability and was classed as
OL,10,Fvulnerable. The bailiff said he didn't
OL,11,Fcare and would take away Adam's
OL,12,Fbelongings regardless.
OL,14,F"The bailiff saying he didn't care -
OL,15,Fwhat cruelty. The enforcement system
OL,16,Fis broken and punishes those already
OL,17,Fstruggling when rules allow such
OL,18,Fpassive, cruel indifference to people
OL,19,Fin crisis."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/8
