OL,6,FMr Charters said the bailiff also
OL,7,Fthreatened to take away Adam's
OL,8,F"government-funded equipment for his
OL,9,Fdisability, a specially adapted
OL,10,Fdevice".
OL,12,FAccording to Citizens Advice, one in
OL,13,Fthree people who have had contact with
OL,14,Fa bailiff have experienced behaviour
OL,15,Fthat breaks Ministry of Justice
OL,16,Fexpectations.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/8
