OL,3,CBailiffs 'threatened to take disabled
OL,4,Cman's equipment'
OL,6,F"And even among the bailiffs that are
OL,7,Fregulated under their current scope,
OL,8,F1% of visits were deemed too
OL,9,Faggressive by the ECB (Enforcement
OL,10,FConduct Board). And by the way, that
OL,11,Fwould equate to hundreds, if not
OL,12,Fthousands of visits a year.
OL,14,F"That is why we need a fair and
OL,15,Fproportionate debt collection system."
OL,17,FMr Charters also referred to another
OL,18,Fconstituent, Michael, a soon-to-be
OL,19,Ffather who was "left without carpet,
OL,20,Fwith a broken bed and a broken boiler".
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/8
