OL,6,FHe said Michael was involved in a
OL,7,F"horrific" motorbike accident which
OL,8,Fleft him "bedridden" and "getting by
OL,9,Fon sick pay alone" after losing his
OL,10,Fjob.
OL,12,F"Michael went from being a homeowner
OL,13,Fwith a near perfect credit score to
OL,14,Fnearly losing everything, and I'm
OL,15,Fpleased to say that he's back on his
OL,16,Ffeet and, although he's still paying
OL,17,Fthe debt off, he is hoping to clear it
OL,18,Fsoon,"
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G7/8
