OL,6,FThe MP concluded his speech by
OL,7,Fsuggesting that while the Enforcement
OL,8,FConduct Board do a good job, there are
OL,9,Fmany bailiffs not in their perimeter.
OL,11,FThe ECB was set up in 2022, with
OL,12,Fministers of the then-Conservative
OL,13,Fgovernment promising to review whether
OL,14,Fit needs to be put on a statutory
OL,15,Ffooting within two years.
OL,17,FHe added: "Statutory regulation would
OL,18,Fenable the ECB to be even more firm
OL,19,Fand drive up standards."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G8/8
